room_title: Escape room "Special Ops: Mysterious Market" by The Escape Game Cincinnati in Cincinnati
room_address: 28 W Freedom Way Suite 300 Cincinnati, OH 45202
room_description: As the closest team of agents in the area, your group has been asked to investigate the Ansar market. The market is closed for the evening and is not known to be a criminal hotspot. However, your “routine check” ends up taking a quick turn and suddenly, the fate of the world rests on your shoulders. With no time to send backup, can you rise to the occasion and save the day?
